{"id": 1644, "date": "1988-09-07T11:00:52", "date_gmt": "1988-09-07T18:00:52", "guid": {"rendered": "http://estreetshuffle.com/?p=1644"}, "modified": "2026-02-25T13:41:22", "modified_gmt": "2026-02-25T21:41:22", "slug": "meeting-across-the-river-rem-and-bruce-springsteen-permanent-vacation", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/1988/09/07/meeting-across-the-river-rem-and-bruce-springsteen-permanent-vacation/", "title": {"rendered": "Permanent Vacation"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p>Seeing R.E.M. perform &#8220;Permanent Vacation&#8221; in concert had to be a thrill for the band&#8217;s fans&#8211;it&#8217;s an obscure pre-label rocker that the band hadn&#8217;t played for 20 years, before they unearthed it briefly in 2003.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/VJzXCdXXiA4?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p>So hearing them play it with Bruce Springsteen on the Vote for Change Tour in 2004? That had to be a pretty amazing moment. Watch it below:</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/ZfxMHXJZdnU?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>Permanent Vacation<br />\nFirst performed:</strong> October 8, 2004 (Orlando, FL)<br />\n<strong>Last performed:</strong> October 8, 2004 (Orlando, FL)</p>\n<p>\u00a9 April 20, 2018</p>\n", "protected": false}, "excerpt": {"rendered": "<p>One time only: Bruce and REM team go old-old-school (in REM years, at least) on &#8220;Permanent Vacation&#8221; at the Orlando Vote for Change show in 2004.</p>\n", "protected": false}, "author": 1, "featured_media": 68022, "comment_status": "open", "ping_status": "open", "sticky": false, "template": "", "format": "standard", "meta": {"_monsterinsights_skip_tracking": false, "_monsterinsights_sitenote_active": false, "_monsterinsights_sitenote_note": "", "_monsterinsights_sitenote_category": 0, "jetpack_post_was_ever_published": false, "_jetpack_newsletter_access": "", "_jetpack_dont_email_post_to_subs": false, "_jetpack_newsletter_tier_id": 0, "_jetpack_memberships_contains_paywalled_content": false, "_jetpack_memberships_contains_paid_content": false, "footnotes": "", "jetpack_publicize_message": "", "jetpack_publicize_feature_enabled": true, "jetpack_social_post_already_shared": true, "jetpack_social_options": {"image_generator_settings": {"template": "highway", "default_image_id": 0, "font": "", "enabled": false}, "version": 2}}, "categories": [3612, 5], "tags": [726, 725], "class_list": ["post-1644", "post", "type-post", "status-publish", "format-standard", "has-post-thumbnail", "hentry", "category-great", "category-meeting-across-the-river", "tag-permanent-vacation", "tag-rem"], "aioseo_notices": [], "jetpack_publicize_connections": [], "jetpack_featured_media_url": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/R-3529230-1334026611.jpg?fit=1198%2C1198&ssl=1", "jetpack_sharing_enabled": true, "jetpack_shortlink": "https://wp.me/p9w3Lk-qw", "jetpack_likes_enabled": true, "jetpack-related-posts": [{"id": 61075, "url": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.p